	1 years of age will not be admitted to this event\, and will not be eligib
	le for a refund. All sales are final. There are no refunds unless the even
	t is cancelled or postponed Opening Acts are subject to change or cancelat
	ion at any time without notice. No refund will be owed if an Opening Act i
	s changed or canceled. Doors times subject to change Tickets may not be re
	sold or offered for resale. If we suspect tickets have been purchased for 
	resale purposes only\, we reserve the right to void or cancel the tickets 
