	er of Glorietta - Sir Woman blends gospel-influenced soul\, Rs warm\, phys
	ical\, and alive. The full band brings weight and swing\, creating shows t
	hat feel loose but intentional\, intimate but loud.Praised by NPR as a bra
	ve new R Sir Womans live performances are about being in the room when it 
	happens - when the band hits\, the groove settles in\, and the night takes
	 on a life of its own.\nThis event is 21 and over. Any ticket holder unabl
