BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0Yc17co6YGiWcS9BulNV7
SUMMARY:Johnny Dynamite\, guests
DTSTAMP:20260404T233136Z
DTSTART:20260724T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $15 ($20.09 after fees)\n\nDay of: $18 ($26.27 after f
	ees)\n\nJohnny Dynamite:\n\nJohnny Dynamite is a Philadelphia based post-p
	unk artist signed to Born Losers Records. Over the course of his first thr
	ee albums\, Johnny Dynamite has emerged as a succinct storyteller and song
	writer. The characters inside Johnny’s dream world are lucid\, manic\, and
	 brimming with pangs of nostalgia. Poised against dark and atmospheric ins
	trumentals\, his harrowed vocal delivery and lyrics paint a picture of los
	t youth\, hopeless romanticism\, and teenage rebellion.\n\nDynamite blends
	 many different genres and connects the dots between different pockets of 
	subculture\; equal parts glossy new wave and anthemic rock n’ roll. Johnny
	’s signature beat centric production style incorporates hard hitting drum 
	machines\, 80’s style guitar riffs and ethereal retro synth patches. His s
	ound has been compared to legacy acts such as Pet Shop Boys\, INXS\, and T
	he Cure as well as more modern acts such as MGMT and M83.\n\nPlease note\,
	 the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+ bar and venue and does not accept ver
	tical ID’s for entry.\n\nhttps://link.dice.fm/Wbd57856287c\n\nFrom Sunset 
	Tavern
URL:https://link.dice.fm/Wbd57856287c
LOCATION:5433 Ballard Avenue Northwest\, Seattle\, Washington 98107\, Unite
	d States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:sunset-tavern
CATEGORIES:Sunset Tavern
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
